											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Yonas notices something behind him and twists to face this new threat, but it's already close and reaching for him. He stumbles to the side, tripping over a root as he tries to dodge a reaching claw, and tumbles down the incline, disappearing into the darkness. [The reaching claw can be cut for cinematic simplicity, the core of it is: &quot;Yonas sees thing, gets spooked, falls down the incline and out of sight.]" />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
